            <title>【评测】Jabra Elite 8 Active 真无线蓝牙耳机　低频特色依旧 + 高频有惊喜 + IP68 防尘防水</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/17/jabra-elite-8-active/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jabra-elite-8-active</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/17/jabra-elite-8-active/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 12:25:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elite 8 Active]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[jabra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Jabra Elite 8 Active]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197800</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">耳机大厂 Jabra 再次推出新款真无线蓝牙耳机，Jabra Elite 8 Active。过去 Jabra 的真无线蓝牙耳机口碑都不俗，尤其受著重低频的用家欢迎。今次推出的 Elite 8 Active，小编试完觉得 Elite 8 Active 承传了 Jabra 的低频表现，而高频方面亦有进步，价钱方面属中价位。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1197878 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09844-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197879 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09904-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>设计简单 </strong><strong>3</strong><strong>种颜色选择 </strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 的设计及外观简约，前方有电量提示，机盒用上了磨砂，手感不错，不易留下指纹等污渍。机底位置有个 USB-C 充电位。Jabra Elite 8 Active 共有 3 款颜色选择，小编拿到的是深灰色，另外有深蓝色，及比较突出焦糖色，小编觉得焦糖色比较特别。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197846 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09842-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active</p><h2><strong>机身只重</strong><strong> 5 克，佩戴感舒适</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">一如既往，Jabra 系列的真无线蓝牙耳机都会随机附送 3 对耳胶，及 1 条耳机同色的 USB-C 充电线。Jabra Elite 8 Active 继续使用入耳式设计，机身质感是液态矽橡胶，主打运动时使用，官方的耳机机身重量为 5 克，小编戴了半天未感不适，感觉非常稳阵，不轻易掉下，加上其防水防尘等级为 IP68，即是完全防尘及可浸入超过一米的水中，用家可安心带住做运动。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197858 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09852-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 随机附送 3 对耳胶，及 1 条耳机同色的 USB-C 充电线</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197847 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09850-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身只重 5 克</p><h2><strong>Jabra Sound+ 可调 EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">操控方面颇为简单，单次按下右边可播放及暂停音乐，单按左边则是切换主动降噪或通透模式。Jabra 向来都有自家应用程式 Jabra Sound+，主要是用来调整主动降噪的程度、通透程度、EQ 等。当中主动降噪及通透都有 5 个程度选择，如用家觉得有压迫感或不适，可以自行调低主动降噪。通透程度则会放大外在声量。EQ 方面就预设 6 项，若用家对 EQ 未有太多认识，想信足够使用。高阶的用家亦可自行调节。另外，Jabra Sound+ 提供了背景功能，用家可以当作背景音，即使不想听音乐，也可以使用耳机专注工作，或达至放松的效果。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197849 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257.jpg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2257-710x1536.jpg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Sound+ 可切换 ANC，通透模式及纯物理隔音</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197848 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258.jpg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2258-710x1536.jpg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Jabra Sound+ 可调 EQ 及背景声</p><h2>Active <strong>Hybird ANC 通话表现良好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 拥有 Active Hybird ANC，即是混合式主动降噪功能，虽然并非 Jabra 耳机中最强科技，但一足够一般情况下使用。耳机内外均有收音咪，处理的噪音频率比一般 ANC 还要阔。Jabra Elite 8 Active  通话表现良好，如果在室内通话并没问题，室外可能偶尔会有风噪声。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197880 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09910-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197850 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09847-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 拥有 Active Hybird ANC，足够应付日常大多数环境</p><h2><strong>支援快速充电，充电 </strong>5 分钟可用 1 小时</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">续航力方面，开启主动降噪后，满电的 Jabra Elite 8 Active 可以连续使 8 小时，连耳机盒则可使用长达 32 小时，都足够小编使用 3 日。而关闭主动降噪则更可分别使用 14 小时及 56 小时，续航力颇长。Jabra Elite 8 Active 如其他耳机般，支援快速充电，只要充电 5 分钟，即可使用 1 小时。总充电时间为  3 小时。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197851 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09856-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jabra Elite 8 Active 支援快速充电，只要充电 5 分钟，即可使用 1 小时</p><h2><strong>Spatial Sound 空间感更阔，睇戏听歌更爽</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Jabra Elite 8 Active 与 Dolby 合作，加入了 Spatial Sound 的功能，令用家有另外的感受，可听到更瞭阔的音场。小编认为适合用来看电影及听现场音乐。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197852 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-470x580.jpg" alt="" width="470" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-470x580.jpg 470w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-730x900.jpg 730w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259-768x947.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2259.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 470px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Spatial Sound 可令用家听到更瞭阔的音场</p><h2><strong>高频人声有惊喜</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小编在 iPhone 上使用 Moov 播放陈柏宇的《尊严》，分别是录音版本及 Fight For ___ Live in Hong Conilseum 演唱会现场版本。小编觉得唱片版本关闭 Spatial Sound 更为适合，高频及人声声音更突出，适合喜欢听 Vocal 的用家。而现场版本开启 Spatial Sound 可能更好，小编颇喜欢 Spatial Sound 带来的现场感。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197853 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2261.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陈柏宇《尊严》（录音版本）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197854 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-310x580.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-310x580.jpg 310w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-481x900.jpg 481w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-768x1438.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260-821x1536.jpg 821w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2260.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 310px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陈柏宇《尊严》（Fight For ___ Live in Hong Conilseum 演唱会现场版本）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">再听听 Mr. 的《边城》，不论歌手声底厚薄，似乎 Elite 8 Active 都演绎得不错，人声依旧突出。低频亦足够份量及下潜力。但《边城》始终是乐队音乐，编曲比较复杂，要求耳机的分析力高，以中价定位的耳机来说，表现合格。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197855 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_2262.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Mr. 《边城》</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Elite 8 Active 与过去的 Jabra 耳机声音上有点分别，除了如以往一样著重低音外，高频方面都下了苦功，令人声高频更出色。整体来说，Elite 8 Active 适合收听流行曲。</p><h2>Spatial Sound <strong>串流播片 </strong><strong>置身现场</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小编使用 Apple TV 串流观看《全面入侵》（Invasion）第一季第一集，未有感到延迟，音色方面造得不俗，开启 Spatial Sound，可使音场更阔，更迫真，彷如置身现场。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1197856 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-1280x709.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-768x425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-1536x850.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.54.31-PM-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《全面入侵》（Invasion）第一季第一集</p><h2><strong>总结： </strong>Spatial Sound 新体验 <strong>高频</strong><strong>音色出众</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Elite 8 Active 的音色比以往的 Jabra 耳机更重视人声，使其整体音色提高了一个层次。Spatial Sound 亦令用家有多个选择，视乎情况和喜好使用。整体而言，Elite 8 Active 适合运动用，亦适合喜爱听高频人声的用家。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

